## Examples of Usage

1. **Personal Projects:**  
   Use this software in your personal projects without any restrictions.  

2. **Commercial Projects:**  
   Incorporate this software into your commercial applications and even sell  
   them, as long as you include the MIT License in your distributed packages.  

3. **Open Source Contributions:**  
   Use this software as a base to create open-source projects, contributing  
   back to the developer community.  


